  "helpJsonDesc": "Ukuze ungenise izinto zokwakha zokufunda njengefayela le-JSON ongazisebenzisa kumodi 3, landela ifomethi elandelayo:",
  "helpJsonTypeSentence": "Umusho (Sentence)",
  "helpJsonTypeWord": "Igama (Word)",
  "helpMode1Desc": "Qala ukufunda izilimi ngendlela enembile kakhulu ngezithonjana zekhibhodi ezinkulu ze-3D nemakrofoni ye-premium.",
  "helpMode1Details": "• Izilungiselelo zolimi: Ungahlola ulimi lwami nolimi engilifundayo ngebhathini lolimi phezulu kwesikrini sasekhaya, futhi ungashintsha ulimi lokufunda.\n• Ukufaka okulula: Faka ngokushesha ngekhibhodi enkulu emaphakathi newindi lombhalo.\n• Qinisekisa izilungiselelo: Ngemva kokuqeda ukufaka, cindezela inkinobho yokuhlola eluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka kwesokudla. Kuzovela iwindi lezilungiselelo ezinemininingwane.\n• Izilungiselelo ezinemininingwane: Ebhokisini lengxoxo elivelayo, ungacacisa iqoqo lezinto ezizogcinwa, amazwana (amanothi) namathegi.\n• Humusha manje: Ngemva kokuqeda izilungiselelo, cindezela inkinobho eluhlaza yokuhumusha ukuze ubuhlakani bokwenziwa buhumushe ngokushesha.\n• Ukusesha okuzenzakalelayo: Ithola futhi ibonise izinguqulo ezifanayo ezikhona ngesikhathi sangempela ngenkathi uthayipha.\n• Lalela futhi ulondoloze: Lalela indlela yokubiza ngezithonjana zesipika ngaphansi kwemiphumela yenguqulo, bese wengeza ohlwini lokufunda ngokuthi 'Londoloza idatha'.",
  "helpMode2Desc": "Bukeza imisho elondoloziwe, bese uhlola ukuthi ukhumbule nge-auto-hide.",
  "helpMode2Details": "• Ukukhetha Incwadi Yokufunda: Sebenzisa imenyu engenhla kwesokudla (⋮) ukuze 'Ukhethe Incwadi Yokufunda' noma 'Ilabhulali Yezinto Eziku-inthanethi'\n• Ukuphenya Ikhadi: Qinisekisa ukuhumusha ngokuthi 'Bonisa/Fihla'\n• Ukulalela: Dlala ukuphinyiselwa ngesithonjana sesipika\n• Ukuqeda Ukufunda: Maka njengokuqediwe ngokuthi uphawu lokuhlola (V)\n• Ukususa: Cindezela isikhathi eside ikhadi ukuze ususe umlando\n• Ukusesha Nokuhlunga: Sekela ibha yokusesha (ukusesha okuhlakaniphile kwesikhathi sangempela) namathegi, isihlungi sezinhlamvu zokuqala",
  "helpMode3Desc": "Lalela umusho bese uwuphinda (Ukushadelwa) ukuze uthuthukise indlela obiza ngayo amagama.",
  "helpMode3Details": "• Khetha Izinto Zokwakha: Khetha iqoqo lezinto zokufunda\n• Setha Isikhawu: Lungisa isikhathi sokulinda phakathi kwemisho ngezinkinobho [-] [+] (3 imizuzwana - 60 imizuzwana)\n• Qala/Misa: Lawula iseshini ye-shadowing\n• Khuluma: Lalela izwi bese ukhuluma ngemuva\n• Impendulo: Amamaki okunemba (0-100) nokuboniswa kombala\n• Izimo Zokusesha: Hlunga izinto ezingapheli ngamathegi, izinto zamuva, izinhlamvu zokuqala",
  "helpNote": "Bhala ngokukhululekile incazelo yegama, imisho eyisibonelo, izimo, njll.",
  "helpNotebook": "Khetha ifolda lapho imiphumela ehunyushiwe izogcinwa khona.",
